Package org.nejjari.hanae.gameup.business

Class GameService

java.lang.Object
org.nejjari.hanae.gameup.business.base.SuperService<GameEntity,GameDto,GameRepository,GameMapper>
org.nejjari.hanae.gameup.business.GameService
@Service @Transactional public class GameService extends SuperService<GameEntity,GameDto,GameRepository,GameMapper>
Service providing business logic and CRUD operations for games. Extends the generic SuperService for GameEntity and GameDto. Handles integration with FastAPI for recommendations and training.
